precis:
INCOME TAX REMISSION ORDER (YUKON TERRITORY LANDS) providing for the
remission of income tax payable by aboriginal peoples in the Yukon who
reside on lands that the Government of Canada has made a commitment to
treat as if they were Indian Reserves for taxation purposes.
